---

<section class="py-24 bg-warm-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-brand-900">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-800/60 text-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">To give every parish a modern, living website — so they can focus on ministry, not technology.</p>

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-warm-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p class="italic text-brand-800/60 leading-relaxed text-lg">"We believe that every parish, regardless of size or budget, deserves a professional online presence. Churchify exists to make that simple, affordable, and stress-free."</p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-semibold text-brand-900">— The Churchify Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
